headline: Amcor to report fiscal 2025 fourth quarter and full year results
summary: Amcor plc (NYSE: AMCR; ASX: AMC) will announce its fiscal 2025 fourth quarter and full year results for the three month and twelve month period ended 30 June 2025, before the US market opens on Thursday 14 August 2025.
